title: The Dangers of Procrastination | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: The Dangers of Procrastination | Joel Osteen
description:
Are you putting off doing something that you know God put in your heart to do? Don't miss out on your opportunity. If you’ll take that step of faith, God will equip you with everything you need to succeed. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
